Quickstrike:





Quickstrike sighed. "Ah gotta get outta here." He stood up, eyeing the three 
now sleeping Predacons for a few seconds, then walked outside. He sat in 
front of a boulder, staring out into the distance. An auto-gun wasn't far 
from him. Megatron and Dark Mouse had done a good job making this cave into 
a base, but it wasn't his type of place.

He put his knees up and rested his arms across them. He was bored and the 
two bragging brothers weren't doing too much for him, except annoy him. He 
leaned his head back until the back of his head hit the long plate behind 
him. He needed something to do, but he couldn't leave the base.
